# Production build wiring. Loaded automatically by `npm run build` (Vite
# production mode). The backend URL is NOT a secret — it's a public
# endpoint the client calls directly, and VITE_-prefixed vars are
# client-exposed by design. The actual secret (FRED_API_KEY) lives only
# in the Render backend environment, never here.
VITE_ARGUS_BACKEND_URL=https://argus-backend-3j2m.onrender.com
